title: Best protein source for hair
description: In monsoon been facing hair fall problem and fizzy dull hair. Then I tried this shampoo and I am so satisfied with the result. It reduced my hairfall to a very great extent after first use itself. Well suited for coloured hair as it’s sulphate free.My hair feel nourished and healthy now.it’s has mild fragrance after use my hair feels very soft without using conditioner.

title: Reduces hairfall
description: I have been using dove shampoo since a long time and it gives wonderful results. It reduces hairfall and gives smooth texture to the hair. Also it is paraben free, without sulphate and dye. Due to early greying of hair I had to use hair color because of which my hair became very rough but thanks to dove shampoo it has again retained its smoothness and shine.

description: What a shampoo! - say goodbye to frizzy and dry hair  and be ready to sport smooth & shiny  hair. Have been using it for past 2 weeks now and the results have been surprisingly amazing. You’ll love the the new hair texture coupled with a very soothing subtle fragrance. With no dyes or other harmful chemicals, this is my definite addition after Dove soaps. Thank you Dove!

title: Nourishment for Dry scalp hair
description: The consistency of shampoo is good and easy to apply all over wet hair. It lathers well. The shampoo leaves my hair soft and silky. It nicely cleans hair and scalp without over drying. You’ll love the the new hair texture coupled with a very soothing subtle fragrance. With no dyes or other harmful chemicals, this is my definite addition after Dove soaps. Thank you Dove!

title: Nourishment for Dry scalp hair
description: The consistency of shampoo is good and easy to apply all over wet hair. It lathers well. The shampoo leaves my hair soft and silky. It nicely cleans hair and scalp without over drying. The scalp feels very fresh and relieved from dryness. Hair smells amazing after wash.It's a good product and I am happy with the results.It is sulphate free. It controls frizziness.

title: Perfect solution  to dry scalp with moisturiser  and nourishment  to hair
description: Everyone wants too shampoo their hair but also to not harm it with the chemicals in it.And this shampoo has no sulphate ,paraben and also dyes free,so it is chemical free and doesn't harm your hair. It helps to reduce the dryness of your scalp and give nourishment  to hair.After using it,it  gives hair shiny,freezy and smoothness. It's smell is nice and lovely. It also helpful  to repairing hair and also Strengthens it

title: Smooth and silky hair in one wash!!!!
description: Well, i have started using this shampoo and the masque for about now 3 months....and i am so damn happy about it. My hair are frizzy and curly, so generally i have to go for keratin treatments...but after using this shampoo and masque i don't need any treatments. As i have colored my hair, so going to spa is must for me to save my hair. I don't like going to saloon for spas n all. But these products have helped me maintain my colored hair as well.

I dont use it often though, just once a week. The fragrance is just amazing. I feel its a bit strong though (but nice), so if u r smell sensitive, then you might not like it.

It doesn't mean that it will make your hair hard, conditioner nourishes your hair well that's why. But the shampoo is great! Mild shampoo.

So transparent that apart from using (or maybe not using) ayurvedic herbs in not more than 1-2% proportions, they have ostensibly answered the major ingredients to be a concoction of chemical through the colour of the shampoo. Results: leave your hair in the driest condition, so much so that even combing it would leave to hairfall due to the stiffness.

It’s not a bad shampoo, it cleans the scalp. But that’s about it. There is nothing special. You can use any shampoo and it will do the same thing. The “intense repair” effect is missing.
